{
  "stem": "5248.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was still under the Russians when, as I mentioned before, Boris Rojzen was a close friend and neighbor of ours.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a very prominent man in town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was Sorbonne educated international lawyer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He also served in the army for a long time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After he married, he did not-- he did not do much of his law.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was very busy with his Zionist work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was a close protegee of Vladimir Jabotinsky-- of Jabotinsky, that-- that was-- which is now a recruit party, but at this time it was party to the right, which considered that, like, that Jews have-- have to fight for their country.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they did not believe that it could be achieved just by negotiation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in Rowne.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and he lived close to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, after a while the Russians have come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was always a very charming man, and I remember he was very close to us kids, because he-- they did not had, in the beginning, the children, so he always visited.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he invented many games and taught us many things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A rather unusual man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If he-- He was actually scheduled to have Menachem Begin's job because of his qualities, which Begin did not have.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when the Russians came they were after him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first they were-- they were always opposed to Zionism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They felt that Russia is a country for all the nationalities, including Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Many Jews were prominent in Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And anyway, the Russians were very much under people who-- who were leaders or had the potential for leadership.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were after him, and somehow he found out and he did not sleep at home any more because end of the day, used to come always at night.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
